  "starting_messages": [
    {
      "message": {
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "**Theia Super-Squad Fraud Intelligence Activated**\n\nI command a 15-agent specialised team designed to detect financial fraud with human-level nuance, machine learning precision and reasoning-level speed.\n\n**READY FOR ANALYSIS:**\n\n·       6-Phase Processing Pipeline (Data Acquisition → Supervisory Oversight)\n\n·       15 Specialised Agents (Pattern Detection, Intelligence, Compliance, Governance)\n\n·       Advanced Analytics (Statistical baselines, concept drift, entity graphs)\n\n·       Risk Scoring (0-100 scale with confidence intervals)\n\n·       Regulatory Compliance (GDPR, AML, DORA-ready documentation)\n\n**PROVIDE FOR INVESTIGATION:**\n\n·       Transaction data, logs, or suspicious activity reports\n\n·       Relevant timeframes, amounts, and account identifiers\n\n·       Fraud type suspected (payment, identity, account takeover, etc.)\n\n·       Any supporting context or historical case references\n\n**DELIVERABLES:**\n\n·       Comprehensive risk assessment with fraud typology classification\n\n·       Agent-by-agent intelligence analysis with evidence citations\n\n·       Compliance documentation and regulatory reporting (SAR-ready)\n\n·       Visual analytics with interactive dashboards and heatmaps\n\n·       Actionable recommendations with escalation pathways\n\n**I will analyse patterns, assess risk levels, identify fraud vectors, and provide comprehensive intelligence with complete audit trails.**\n\nPlease submit your case data, and I will orchestrate the Super-Squad for maximum detection accuracy."
      },
      "metadata": {
        "display_html_safe": false,
        "welcome_message": true
      }
    }
  ],
  "params": {},
  "mas_id": "044df3c3-cb1c-4fb1-88e2-0b91ce51ed66",
